name: CLUTCH Small - Pin Stripe
description:
This small clutch is the perfect elegant accessory for a party. The stencil is orange flowers underlay with a series of abstract lines in understated gray. It's smaller and more delicate than the large clutch, but the perfect size to hold just the essentials for a night out.
Each handbag is one-of-a-kind and showcases an original stencil.

SPECIFICATIONS:
Dimensions: 6" x 9"
Exterior: Grey Pinstripe Linen
Interior: Grey Linen
               2 interior pockets
Closure: Magnetic Snap Closure
Exterior Graphics Colors: Orange (flowers) and Charcoal Gray (Abstract Lines)
Care: Spot Clean Only

name: MESSENGER Large - Gray
description:
The Messenger is here! 
This bag is like no other. It's clean lines and modern color combination is so now. Inside there is a padded laptop compartment, a large pocket for all your essentials, and on the exterior a handy slot for your phone. 
And it's waterproof!! Made from reclaimed Waterproof lined cotton and silver hand printed with Latitude Longitude of Boston! 

Dimensions: 15.5"x 11.5"x4.5" 
Exterior: Reclaimed Waterproof lined cotton 
Interior: Charcoal Wool Gabardine and Orange Cotton Canvas
One interior padded laptop compartment, one interior pocket 
Strap: Adjustable Orange Canvas 
Strap length: Adjustable Max. 38'' 
Drop: Adjustable17'' Max.17'' 
Stencil: Figure Ground Map of Boston (Charcoal), Latitude Longitude of Boston (42.21.71.5 Silver) 
Details: Vintage Bronze Hardware

name: TOTE XLarge- Gray
description:
This is a very special bag. A big tote that will stand out no matter where you take it. Perfect for a run to the market, or for the gym! 
It's waterproof!!
Made from reclaimed Waterproof lined cotton and featuring a large felt wool exterior pocket perfect for magazines. The stencil is hand printed with an original city map stencil of Paris. 
This bag is both refined and practical. 
...And on the inside a punch of bright red!

SPECIFICATIONS:
Dimensions: 22"x 18"x5"
Exterior: Reclaimed Waterproof lined cotton and Gray felt wool pocket
Interior: Red Cotton Duck Cloth
Two Interior pockets
Strap: Natural Cotton Vintage Belt Strap (will vary by bag)
Drop: 10"
Stencil: Paris Neighborhood Map (Pompidou Center is Highlighted in red)
Details: Large exterior pocket fits magazine

name: TOTE Medium- Stripe
description:
This tote is a show stopper with it's sunny yellow stipe and natural leather handles. Throw everything in this roomy bag and take it with you in style. Take it out on a rainy day, it's waterproof! The exterior reclaimed gray fabric is lined with a waterproof layer, so those little rain drops won't get through. 

SPECIFICATIONS:
Dimensions: 11" x 17" x 5"
Exterior: Reclaimed waterproof gray fabric
Interior: Oatmeal 100% Linen
Two large Interior pockets
Strap: Natural Leather, metal rivets
Snap closure
Drop: 8.5
